Package edu.caltech.nanodb.sqlparse

This package contains all of the classes for SQL lexing and parsing in NanoDB.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NanoSqlParserTokenTypes  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NanoSqlLexer
    A lexer for tokenizing SQL commands into various tokens necessary for parsing.
    NanoSqlParser
    A parser for processing SQL commands into the various command-classes derived from Command.

Package edu.caltech.nanodb.sqlparse Description

This package contains all of the classes for SQL lexing and parsing in NanoDB. At this point, all of the classes are generated by ANTLR, so don't expect these classes to contain very much javadoc documentation. They will contain as much as reasonable, though.
